<bug>
    <id>276552</id>
    <title>"Default Browser" setting does not capture MHT</title>
    <description>
        <paragraph id="1">
            <sentence id="1.1">I saved a page as an "archive" page from IE.</sentence>
            <sentence id="1.2">Later I installed Firefox and
later still told Firefox (via tools/options/general) to check to see if it is
the default browser.</sentence>
        </paragraph>
        <paragraph id="2">
            <sentence id="2.1">So now Firefox is my default browser for opening HTM, HTML files and URLs handed
off by my newsgroups program.</sentence>
            <sentence id="2.2">But clicking on my saved MHT file opens IE.</sentence>
            <sentence id="2.3">The
default capture did not pick up MHT files.</sentence>
        </paragraph>
        <paragraph id="3">
            <sentence id="3.1">I suspect that this is an oversight on the "check to see if it is the default
browser" action.</sentence>
        </paragraph>
    </description>
</bug>
